comments: Sabonis (IND) does not maintain verticality as he makes contact  to Barnes' (SAC) head that affects his driving shot attempt.
Hield (SAC) makes marginal contact to Oladipo's arm and does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Sabonis (IND) makes contact with Barnes' (SAC) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Hield (SAC) cleanly dislodges the ball from Oladipo (IND) at the end of his drive.
Oladipo (IND) gives Holmes (SAC) room to avoid the contact as he establishes himself in a screening position.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of defensive goaltending on Holmes (SAC) is overturned.
Sabonis (IND) absorbs the contact from Fox (SAC) and the contact is marginal during his driving shot attempt.
Brogdon (IND) makes contact to Holmes' (SAC) arm that affects his control of the ball after securing the rebound.
Sabonis (IND) engages and disengages with Barnes (SAC) during the pick.
Brogdon (IND) makes marginal contact to Fox's (SAC) body during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Sabonis (IND) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Barnes (SAC) and absorbs the contact.
Oladipo (IND) intentionally lifts his leg and makes contact with the ball.
McDermott (IND) makes contact to Holmes (SAC) arm that affects his FOM.
Sabonis (IND) cleanly dislodges the ball from Holmes (SAC) during the rebound.
Holiday (IND) commits a take foul on Haliburton (SAC).
Fox (SAC) commits a take foul on Brogdon (IND).
Barnes (SAC) makes contact to Oladipo's (IND) arm that affects his jump shot attempt.
Brogdon (IND) commits a take foul on Joseph (SAC).
